## Non-functional requirements
- **Responsive size matrix:** iPhone SE, iPhone 16 Pro, iPhone 16 Pro Max, iPad;
  small/Pixel/tablet Android; each at textScale 1.0 and 2.0. **Zero render
  (overflow) errors on any.**
- **Accessibility:** Semantics on interactive elements, WCAG AA, ≥48dp targets,
  survives textScale 2.0, respects reduce-motion.
- **Localization:** <languages> · all strings via ARB · RTL-safe.
- **Performance:** lazy lists, off-isolate heavy work, cached/resized images.
- **Security:** secure token storage, owner-scoped backend rules, no secrets in
  repo.

